title: Backstroke of the West [2005] [Revenge of the Sith] x264 1080p.m
description:
These are the hilarious subs for "Star Wars: Episode III - Revenge of the Sith" that went through some English-to-Chinese-to-English translation resulting in only about 3 subtitle lines matching what's being said. 
We wanted to put these glorious subs on a good raw, so we used a 1080p BRRip. We styled the subs, and while we were at it, added some special effects.
